{"tid":2461084,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經新聞：智將基金「連燈力」呂布軍盤前以$2.25進軍妖股CIDM，武勇還是智障？","createTime":"2021-03-25T08:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T09:28:02.000Z","uid":149018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"48798e5730f4f9c1483bda2666395cc133f7dd87","tid":2461084,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:20:18.000Z","msg":"第二十三次軍議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2460685/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRMGHqw6Ajn4mQxurN32yds53PV7YJ2wGxpr978bGwReu?filename=dutDcyr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdutDcyr.jpg&h=ae6cf78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPSQNiA19kwDB81qDDzYt6ZYfubMjFoZ1u9TUdJKaUVFZ?filename=DWt0qTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDWt0qTs.jpg&h=629e6423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYAKLTs1oARvxHS5qqTRKfyew3ZACYvtYhQctwcAGSscq?filename=MhbUvj7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhbUvj7.jpg&h=879f1d31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWCPPuzuoFKdJWHHxokkc5azGhuLyJ5Brv5SLAXCzjVKx?filename=9Q19jdq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Q19jdq.jpg&h=ff393b35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二十二戰，呂布於盤前$11.19進攻SOXS受眾軍師武將所指被人恥笑，開市後一度下趺10%但大睡一場清晨軍隊已$11.82戰勝SOXS。但可惜勝利所帶來之傷亡(奉先倉)卻傷亡慘重....<br />\n<br />\n第二十三戰軍議，呂布以神之手抽出CIDM妖股，以$2.25進攻恐非最佳時機，但昨SOXS卻同樣道理。奉先以$2作退兵之地，望不用退兵...<br />\n<br />\n呂布軍「連燈力」目前戰況22戰9勝13敗，勝率現為40.9%！<br />\n目前「連燈力」呂布狀態：<br />\n武力100 智力78(Fear a lot)，「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">879.08</span>HP 累計虧損-<span class=\"red\">12.09</span>%<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呂布曰：又計錯數變注資$18.67 好憎我自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrxwxC2aadyVAcF23ujN8rQFVkbHWene6UnuTGy6Pxeq?filename=XBRdLWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXBRdLWn.jpg&h=fba41da2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3160e685c2022d27d018912955f57ae9e15a386","tid":2461084,"uid":13731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"智障"},{"pid":"418a198a77ecfedf0aeec8d9ec862e497663926e","tid":2461084,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7e0223679c039685af3fd8af8adb40c6ab9fff","tid":2461084,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3160e685c2022d27d018912955f57ae9e15a386","tid":2461084,"uid":13731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:20:44.000Z","msg":"智障"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"今仗好恐怖呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71c09baad098cbac12d1110b82b84f6253c0a58","tid":2461084,"uid":155559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:25:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />慘"},{"pid":"0d5225f4d9265ca21e6c9889cbb515d4559fbc36","tid":2461084,"uid":248536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"Snes更稱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f464e585b3977cccdcc042f994d72e3f2c49fe3","tid":2461084,"uid":160891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"奉先將軍竟劍指細價盤，<br />\n好易-50%架波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14532535b10417cbbbe2eda79739685c12b347c","tid":2461084,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite